---
description: Do not attribute commits or PRs to Cursor Agent
alwaysApply: true
---

# No Cursor Agent attribution

- Never add `Co-authored-by: Cursor`, `Co-authored-by: Cursor Agent`, `cursoragent@cursor.com`, or `Made-with: Cursor` to commits, PRs, or code comments.
- Never set git author/committer to Cursor Agent.
- Commits must use the repository owner's git identity only (`BabinRR` / configured `user.name` and `user.email`).
